### mounts filesystems at boot
cat /etc/fstab

[Storgae Device]                                 [Mount Point]    [Filesystem Type]     [Mount Options]
/dev/sda1                                        /boot            ext4                  defaults 0 0

### Mount with UUID
UUID=d9de98bc-2043-4fa4-9b98-49b993d70e29        /mnt/xfs         xfs                   defaults 0 0

### Mount with LABEL (make lable with e2label)
LABEL=EXT3                                       /mnt/ext3        ext3                  defaults 0 0

### Mount with storage device path
/dev/sdb3                                        /mnt/ext4        ext4                  defaults 0 0

### Mount swap
LABEL=SWAP                                       swap             swap                  defaults 0 0
